    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### ⚙️ Step 2 — Fetch & filter n8n workflows\nRetrieves all workflows from this n8n instance via API.\n\nThe **Filter Changed Files** node compares each workflow's byte size against the file size stored on GitHub. Only workflows that are **new or modified** pass through — skipping unchanged ones avoids unnecessary GitHub commits.",
        "height": 268,
        "width": 820,
        "color": "#FFFFFF"
      },
      "id": "b94d3fa6-84b1-49d4-b97f-8c04cc7bd707",
