          "content": "### 💾 Step 3 — Commit files to GitHub\nFor each changed workflow:\n1. Build the target filename and commit timestamp\n2. Check if the file already exists in the repo\n3. **Update** it (edit) if it exists, or **Create** it (upload) if it's new\n\nFiles are named: `workflow-name.json` (lowercase, hyphenated)",
